---
By: Rainer Maria Rilke
Source:
  ID: 631057a1-0221-4885-ba61-78b661b62b70
  Source:
    Title: Letter to COuntess Margot Sizzo-Noris-Crouy
    Locus:
      Date: April 12, 1922
  Locus:
    Daily: November 20
Title: Paintings
---
I am most struck by the small paintings you sent. I experience in them your
old form, in miniature, where vast inner space is mirrored, where even winter
and snow (and we have our share of both!) bespeak huge distance and wandering,
the freshness and joy of pure undiluted youth.
